sql:
SELECT P.product_name, S.size_name 
FROM products P
JOIN sizes S ON P.size_id = S.size_id;

external_knowledge:
- 'Typical waist and length measurements': refers to the average values of waist_cm and length_cm; 
- 'American sizing system': refers to the 'US' standard name in the database; 
- 'Currently available items': products with an active status, i.e., is_active = 1.
